{"tid":481450,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"喺工廈番工／出入嘅巴絲入一入黎","createTime":"2017-11-27T07:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T08:39:27.000Z","uid":146274,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"804988971c667cf9fcf466b5b6e8457250b85d0a","tid":481450,"uid":146274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T07:44:29.000Z","msg":"大家好，小弟係一個滿懷理想同熱誠嘅有為青年，矢志為香港工廈發展出一分微力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位出入工廈嘅巴打／絲打，可以的話幫幫手填份問卷，支持下。<br />\n填黎做乜恕我不能透露，只可以話，份報告寫左出黎會有大粒野見到，希望大家可以多多支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/LPAYZ9DVoviAEbDm1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FLPAYZ9DVoviAEbDm1&d=RF7omOGQ%2B7%2FbDvLEXCBJ7m6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=cb8fa51d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/LPAYZ9DVoviAEbDm1</a><br />\n<br />\nJ圖後補，因為番緊工。萬分感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0b25ddf14862c5ac53b1d5e5373ebd95ecce3a","tid":481450,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T07:49:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf2b0f7df1b9e1c8cb221ed867cc0537bbb4f717","tid":481450,"uid":120199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T07:53:27.000Z","msg":"鬼鬼地 唔填"},{"pid":"8f6721d68e0adccd5b51e5d1aa876de3a8adf3f6","tid":481450,"uid":146274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T07:54:46.000Z","msg":"點鬼法呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db835850d5cd9722e49ff6611b032638821e6518","tid":481450,"uid":146274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T08:56:41.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ecc6796566d2d819ea9f1b93a5a0306282520e49","tid":481450,"uid":146274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T09:34:45.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7462587fa2c235e036db58b7d309de85c5f62795","tid